Hoopoe — macOS Electron desktop cockpit for the Agentic Coding Flywheel.

Hoopoe is unreleased while the project is pre-Phase-1; no copyright notice for
Hoopoe's own code is included here yet.

THIRD-PARTY ATTRIBUTIONS
========================

t3code (https://github.com/pingdotgg/t3code)
--------------------------------------------
The desktop scaffolding (Electron lifecycle, auth bridge, settings system,
keybindings + AST, build pipeline) is vendored from t3code under the MIT
License. Copies of lifted files live under
`apps/desktop/src/vendored/t3code/` with the MIT notice preserved at the top
of each file. The verbatim t3code MIT license text is preserved at
`apps/desktop/src/vendored/t3code/LICENSE`.

  License: MIT
  Copyright (c) 2026 T3 Tools Inc.
  Pinned commit: see `docs/source-provenance.md`

Adaptations to lifted t3code files (rebranding, schema swaps, daemon-launch
wiring, monolith decomposition) live in Hoopoe's own files that import from
`vendored/`. We do not edit `vendored/` files in place beyond mechanical mass
renames; this keeps the diff against upstream small enough to re-merge later
if needed. See `plan.md` Appendix B for the file inventory.
